            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the green stalk off your<strong> aubergine[s] </strong>and discard, then chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into wedges</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped aubergine</strong> and<strong> red onion wedges</strong> to the dish</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1632393625522-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
