            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[400ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> balsamic vinegar </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>dried basil </strong>and <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano </strong>to the dish</p><p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 45 min or until the veg is tender and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>baked plant-based ratatouille</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632393636358-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
