            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1632393636358-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the plant-based ratatouille has been cooking for 10 min, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof</strong> <strong>dish</strong> with the <strong>saffron</strong>, a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong>, making sure all the rice is submerged</p><p>Cover very tightly with <strong>tin</strong> <strong>foil</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 30 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>saffron rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1632393641188-x200.jpg",
