            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, remove the <strong>baked</strong> <strong>plant-based ratatouille</strong> from the oven and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p><p>Set the <strong>plant-based ratatouille</strong> in the centre of the table, ready to share</p><p>Tear your <strong>basil leaves </strong>all over the top and serve the <strong>saffron rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Let everyone dig in!</p>",
      "order": 8,
